<section class="pg-section" data-section="What To Expect During Your 60-Minute Microneedling Experience">
  <h2 class="pg-h">What To Expect During Your 60-Minute Microneedling Experience</h2>
  <p class="pg-text">Every step is designed for your comfort and results. Here's exactly what happens during your 60-minute treatment at our Millburn spa.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Consultation &amp; Skin Assessment (5-10 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">We start with a thorough consultation to understand your skin goals and concerns. Our expert esthetician analyzes your skin type, texture, and problem areas to create a customized microneedling plan just for you.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Deep Cleansing &amp; Preparation (10-15 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Your skin is gently cleansed to remove all makeup, oils, and impurities. This ensures your pores are perfectly prepped for treatment and maximizes the absorption of healing serums during microneedling.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Numbing Cream Application (15-20 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">We apply a topical numbing cream to ensure your complete comfort during treatment. You'll relax while the cream takes effect, making your microneedling experience virtually pain-free.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Microneedling Treatment (20-30 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Using our advanced microneedling device, we create tiny micro-channels in your skin that trigger natural collagen production. Most clients describe it as a light tingling sensation. We apply nourishing serums that penetrate deep for maximum results.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Calming Serum &amp; Post-Treatment Care (5-10 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">We finish with a soothing, hydrating serum to calm your skin and accelerate healing. You'll receive personalized aftercare instructions to protect your results and maximize your glow in the days ahead.</p>
  <a class="pg-btn" href="/microneedling-millburn-nj">Schedule Now</a>
